<plot>A short film of three individual stories separated by color. Each story uniquely describes the state of being left alone in one form or another. In the first scene, a girl ('yellow') searches for her brother in woods and fields. The second, a small child ('red') is left alone when his friend retires for the evening from the playground. And finally, the third story tells about an elderly woman ('blue') with a cat that wonders off to disappear. Each character explores their surroundings before being confronted by creatures to fill the void of loneliness.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?187856</url></doc>
